biography: Dr. Harald Bosch is a senior consultant at Novatec Consulting GmbH where he is coordinating the topic machine learning and artificial intelligence. Prior to this, he was a post doc researcher at the university of Stuttgart where he developed visual analytics solutions for complex domain problems, bringing together information visualization, human computer interaction and data mining.
